Quote:  [Headline] Kathleen Mavourneen Stakes [sub] Sheehan a Sure Starter 	... Sheehan did not exhibit any intention of worrying, and when sentenced to twelve months and labelled as an habitual criminal, which at his age (63) means life, he passed down the trap feeling apparently relieved.
